Title: Outlander
Actors: Caitriona Balfe, Sam Heughan, Tobias Menzies, Tobias Menzies, Graham McTavish, Stephen Martin Walters, Grant O'Rourke, Duncan Lacroix, Nell Hudson, Annette Badland, Lotte Verbeek, Gary Lewis
Plot: Follows the story of Claire Randall, a married combat nurse from 1945 who is mysteriously swept back in time to 1743, where she is immediately thrown into an unknown world where her life is threatened. When she is forced to marry Jamie Fraser, a chivalrous and romantic young Scottish warrior, a passionate relationship is ignited that tears Claire's heart between two vastly different men in two irreconcilable lives.
